ng's optical depth in\nthese regions ranges from 1.5 to almost 5. This suggests that the total mass of\nthe B ring is most likely between one-third and two-thirds the mass of Saturn's\nmoon Mimas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 00:30:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2016 22:41:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-31"}
