ces allows us to deduce properties of the value function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 15:32:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2016 11:36:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-04"}
